      <guid>//localhost:1313/posts/8bill-stronger/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h4 id=&#34;castgarden-video&#34;&gt;CastGarden Video&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;iframe title=&#34;8 Billion Stronger Versions&#34; width=&#34;100%&#34; height=&#34;450&#34; src=&#34;https://cast.garden/videos/embed/b1a62d25-407e-4d89-ae1d-c1e9e7493569&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34; allowfullscreen=&#34;&#34; sandbox=&#34;allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-popups&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;click-here-to-watch-this-video-on-torhttpcastgardn7yj746n7nyt3udot5orhpqfs36sl7rq2y3yd4su6ruuddydonionwnwkcsoj4zthzyqu2tpbg4k&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://castgardn7yj746n7nyt3udot5orhpqfs36sl7rq2y3yd4su6ruuddyd.onion/w/nWkCSoj4ZThZyqu2TpBG4k&#34;&gt;Click here to watch this video on Tor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Orinally published December 2023&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&#xA;58 yrs ago Paul Harvey broadcast his &amp;ldquo;Freedom to Chains&amp;rdquo; monologue. People didn&amp;rsquo;t realize just how prophetic it was. Everything he talked about in it came to fruition. Fast forward to today and we have people such as Chris Webby and Oliver Anthony not mincing words while calling out the &amp;ldquo;Rich Men North of Richmond&amp;rdquo;. People all over the world are having a &amp;ldquo;Panic Attack&amp;rdquo; while living in their little &amp;ldquo;Fantasy&amp;rdquo; bubbles.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
